    "en": {
      "title": "National Fuel Pass QR program island-wide implementation from 25th July",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Fuel Pass QR program will be implemented across the Island from Monday, the 25th of July, tweeted Minister Kanchana Wijesekera.",
        "He said that a Pilot Project will be conducted in multiple locations in Colombo from the 21st July along with the last digit of the number plate for QR Quota.",
        "The Minister said that the QR Code will be tested at multiple locations in Colombo 21-24th July.",
        "Changes to the last Digit of Number Plate for Fueling \u2013 Will be effective from 21st July, Island wide.",
        "National Fuel Pass QR program island-wide implementation from 25th July",
        "Sri Lanka crisis: India calls all-party meet on Tuesday (19)"
      ],
